史東于2017年出演的電影只有運動劇情片《[[勝負反手拍|勝負反手拍]]》，該片改編自1973年網球選手[[比莉·珍·金|金恩夫人]]（史東飾演）和[[鮑比·里格斯|鮑比·里格斯]]（{{lang|en|Bobby Riggs}}，史提夫·卡爾飾演）之間的[[雌雄争霸战_(網球)|比賽]]。在準備的過程中，史東跟金見面，觀賞以前的片段並對她進行訪問，同時跟隨方言教練去訓練以金的口音説話，而且飲用高熱量的蛋白質奶昔使自己增加{{convert|15|lb}}<ref>{{cite news|last1=Coggan|first1=Devan|title=Emma Stone on Preparing to Play Billie Jean King: 'I Was a Real Creep'|url=http://ew.com/movies/2017/08/15/emma-stone-battle-of-the-sexes-interview/|accessdate=2017-09-20|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2017-08-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921000701/http://ew.com/movies/2017/08/15/emma-stone-battle-of-the-sexes-interview/|archivedate=2017-09-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Randone|first1=Amanda|title=How Emma Stone Gained 15 Pounds for Battle of the Sexes|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/881311/how-emma-stone-gained-15-pounds-for-battle-of-the-sexes|publisher=E!|accessdate=2017-09-20|date=2017-09-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170919205622/http://www.eonline.com/news/881311/how-emma-stone-gained-15-pounds-for-battle-of-the-sexes|archivedate=2017-09-19}}</ref>。電影在[[2017年多倫多國際影展|2017年多倫多國際影展]]首映，並獲得高度好評，而部分影評人認為這是史東演藝生涯中最好的演出<ref>{{cite web|last1=Giles|first1=Jeff|title=American Made Is Certified Fresh|url=https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/article/american-made-is-certified-fresh/|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2017-12-20|date=2017-09-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171126190012/https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/article/american-made-is-certified-fresh/|archivedate=2017-11-26}}</ref>。《衛報》的班傑明·李讚賞她能飾演完全不同的類型，並讚許其演技「强而有力」且「令人信服」<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lee|first1=Benjamin|title=Battle of the Sexes review – Emma Stone serves up rousing, timely tennis drama|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/sep/11/battle-of-the-sexes-review-toronto-film-festival-tiff|accessdate=2017-09-20|work=The Guardian|date=2017-09-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170919185458/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/sep/11/battle-of-the-sexes-review-toronto-film-festival-tiff|archivedate=2017-09-19}}</ref>。就算這樣，電影的收入依舊比預算2500萬美元要少<ref>{{cite news|author=Ende, Maura|title='Battle of the Sexes' has important messages about prejudice, sexuality|url=https://buffalonews.com/2017/10/11/battle-sexes-important-messages-prejudice-sexuality/|work=The Buffalo News|date=2017-10-11|accessdate=2018-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180920084021/https://buffalonews.com/2017/10/11/battle-sexes-important-messages-prejudice-sexuality/|archive-date=2018-09-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。史東憑著該片四度入圍金球獎，並與金共同出席典禮<ref>{{cite magazine |last1=Pett |first1=Stephanie |title=Emma Stone Brings Billie Jean King, Who She She Played in Battle of the Sexes, as Globes Date |url=https://people.com/movies/golden-globes-2018-emma-stone-brings-billie-jean-king/ |accessdate=2018-09-08 |magazine=People |date=2018-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180908164839/https://people.com/movies/golden-globes-2018-emma-stone-brings-billie-jean-king/ |archive-date=2018-09-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2018年，史東和[[瑞秋·懷茲|瑞秋·懷茲]]在歷史劇情片《[[真寵|真寵]]》中主演表姐妹[[阿比蓋爾·瑪莎姆|阿比蓋爾·瑪莎姆]]（{{lang|en|Abigail Masham}}）和[[馬爾博羅公爵夫人薩拉·丘吉爾|薩拉·丘吉爾]]（{{lang|en|Sarah Churchill}}），爲了奪取[[安妮_(英國女王)|安妮女王]]（[[奧莉薇雅·柯爾曼|-{zh-tw:奧莉薇雅·柯爾曼;zh-hk:奧莉菲亞·高文;zh-cn:奥利维娅·科尔曼;}-]]飾演）的寵愛而作鬥爭。史東對於作爲英國演員中唯一的美國人感到有挑戰性，並很難掌握英式口音<ref>{{cite news |last1=Galloway |first1=Stephen |title=Telluride: Emma Stone Reveals Her Acting Breaking Points |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/emma-stones-reveals-acting-breaking-points-1139241 |accessdate=2018-09-06 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2018-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180904190438/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/emma-stones-reveals-acting-breaking-points-1139241 |archive-date=2018-09-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影於8月在[[第75屆威尼斯影展|第75屆威尼斯影展]]舉行首映<ref>{{cite magazine |first=Ariston |last=Anderson |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/venice-film-festival-unveils-full-lineup-1129426 |title=Venice to Kick Off Awards Season With New Films From Coen Brothers, Luca Guadagnino and Alfonso Cuaron |magazine=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2018-07-25 |accessdate=2018-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725121213/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/venice-film-festival-unveils-full-lineup-1129426 |archive-date=2018-07-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]的麥可·努丁（{{lang|en|Michael Nordine}}）讚賞史東在《[[樂來越愛你|樂來越愛你]]》之後接演金髮角色，並把三位女主演稱爲「在時代作品中即悲慘又滑稽的雄偉三巨頭」<ref>{{cite web |last1=Nordine |first1=Michael |title='The Favourite' Review: Yorgos Lanthimos' Royal Drama Is His Crowning Achievement — Venice |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2018/08/the-favourite-review-yorgos-lanthimos-emma-stone-venice-1201998762/ |publisher=IndieWire |accessdate=2018-09-07 |date=2018-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180907221353/https://www.indiewire.com/2018/08/the-favourite-review-yorgos-lanthimos-emma-stone-venice-1201998762/ |archive-date=2018-09-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。史東憑著《真寵》分別五度入圍金球獎和三度入圍奧斯卡獎<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/golden-globe-nominations-2019-1203082075/|title=Golden Globe Nominations: Complete List|date=2018-12-06|work=Variety|access-date=2018-12-06|archive-date=2019-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190202054004/https://variety.com/2018/film/news/golden-globe-nominations-2019-1203082075/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/oscar-nominations-2019-complete-list-nominees-1172407|title=Oscars: Nominations List|date=2019-01-22|work=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=2019-01-22|archive-date=2019-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122160706/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/oscar-nominations-2019-complete-list-nominees-1172407|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該年9月，史東在[[網飛|網飛]]黑色幽默迷你劇《[[狂想_(電視劇)|狂想]]》中出演並擔任執行製作人，並同喬納·希爾演對手戲，該劇由[[凱瑞·福永|凱瑞·福永]]執導。史東和希爾飾演兩名陌生人安妮·蘭茲伯（{{lang|en|Annie Landsberg}}）和歐文·米爾格里姆（{{lang|en|Owen Milgrim}}），他們的生活因神秘的藥物試驗而改變。因爲是福永作品的傾慕者，所以史東在未閲讀劇本的情況下就同意參演<ref>{{cite web |last1=Jeffery |first1=Morgan |title=Emma Stone opens up about Maniac rewrites |url=http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/ustv/news/a866529/emma-stone-maniac-netflix-interview/ |website=Digital Spy |accessdate=2018-09-21 |date=2018-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180921191143/http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/ustv/news/a866529/emma-stone-maniac-netflix-interview/ |archive-date=2018-09-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《衛報》的露西·孟甘（{{lang|en|Lucy Mangan}}）讚賞史東和希爾飾演與自己大相徑庭的角色，並給出職業生涯中最棒的演出<ref>{{cite news |last1=Mangan |first1=Lucy |title=Maniac review – Jonah Hill and Emma Stone hit career highs in NYC dystopia |url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2018/sep/21/maniac-review-jonah-hill-emma-stone-netflix-cary-fukunaga |accessdate=2018-09-21 |work=The Guardian |date=2018-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180921075620/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2018/sep/21/maniac-review-jonah-hill-emma-stone-netflix-cary-fukunaga |archive-date=2018-09-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；而《[[時代雜誌|時代]]》的朱迪·伯曼（{{lang|en|Judy Berman}}）同樣對於他們從《男孩我最壞》之後的成長感到印象深刻，並注意到他們演出的複雜性<ref>{{cite magazine |last1=Berman |first1=Judy |title=Maniac Is the Most Exciting Netflix Drama Since Stranger Things |url=http://time.com/5400995/maniac-netflix-review-emma-stone-jonah-hill/ |accessdate=2018-09-21 |magazine=Time |date=2018-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180921123618/http://time.com/5400995/maniac-netflix-review-emma-stone-jonah-hill/ |archive-date=2018-09-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年，史東出演[[保罗·麦卡特尼|保罗·麦卡特尼]]歌曲《[[誰在乎|誰在乎]]》（{{lang|en|Who Cares}}）的音樂錄影帶<ref>{{cite news |last1=Grow |first1=Kory |title=See Paul McCartney, Emma Stone Shrug Off Bullies in ‘Who Cares’ Video |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/see-paul-mccartney-emma-stone-shrug-off-bullies-in-who-cares-video-771060/ |work=Rolling Stone |date=2018-12-19 |accessdate=2019-03-11 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605062109/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/see-paul-mccartney-emma-stone-shrug-off-bullies-in-who-cares-video-771060/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2019年至2020年，史東在《[[喪屍樂園：連環屍殺|喪屍樂園：連環屍殺]]》重演角色威奇托（{{lang|en|Wichita}}），電影所獲評價褒貶不一，並在全球取得1億1200萬美元票房<ref>{{cite web |title= Zombieland: Double Tap (2019) |website= Rotten Tomatoes |url= https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/zombieland_double_tap/ |accessdate= 2019-11-14 |archive-date= 2019-11-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191113164003/https://rottentomatoes.com/m/zombieland_double_tap/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url= https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt1560220/ |title= Zombieland: Double Tap (2019) |website= Box Office Mojo |access-date= 2020-01-17 |archive-date= 2019-11-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191102113102/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt1560220/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。她還為網絡紀錄連續劇《[[头脑解密|-{zh-cn:头脑解密; zh-tw:腦內解碼; zh-hk:腦內解碼;}-]]》（{{lang|en|''The Mind, Explained''}}）作旁白和在《古魯家族》[[古魯家族：新石代|續集]]繼續聲演角色「-{zh-cn:小伊; zh-tw:一妹; zh-hk:阿葉;}-」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vox.com/2019/9/12/20861728/the-mind-explained-netflix-vox|title=The mind, explained in five 20-minute Netflix episodes|author=Gordon, Claire|date=2019-09-12|website=Vox|access-date=2020-05-07|archive-date=2020-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200507031645/https://www.vox.com/2019/9/12/20861728/the-mind-explained-netflix-vox|url-status=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Kroll |first1=Kroll |title='Croods 2,' Revived as Animated Sequel, and Jason Blum's 'Spooky Jack' Get Release Dates |url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/croods-2-spooky-jack-release-dates-1202563635/ |access-date=2019-01-16 |website=Variety |date=2017-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604034547/https://variety.com/2017/film/news/croods-2-spooky-jack-release-dates-1202563635/ |archive-date=2019-06-04 |url-status=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|title='Sing 2' To Croon Summer 2021; 'The Croods 2' Moves To Holiday Season 2020|url=https://deadline.com/2019/04/sing-2-croods-2-release-date-changes-1202594951/|access-date=2019-07-05|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828024514/https://deadline.com/2019/04/sing-2-croods-2-release-date-changes-1202594951/|archive-date=2019-08-28|url-status=no}}</ref>。

2021年，史東在《[[101忠狗|101忠狗]]》真人衍生作品《[[時尚惡女：庫伊拉|時尚惡女：庫伊拉]]》飾演[[庫伊拉·狄薇|庫伊拉·狄薇]]（{{lang|en|Cruella de Vil}}，原飾演者為[[101忠狗|1996年改編版]]的[[葛倫·克蘿絲|-{zh-cn:格伦·克洛斯; zh-tw:葛倫·克蘿絲; zh-hk:格蓮·高絲;}-]]），她還與-{zh-cn:克洛斯; zh-tw:克蘿絲; zh-hk:高絲;}-共同擔任執行製片<ref>{{cite web |last1=D'Alessandro |first1=Anthony |title=Disney Puts A Slew Of Dates On Hold For 'Jungle Book 2', 'Maleficent 2', 'Dumbo', 'Cruella' & More |url=https://deadline.com/2016/04/disney-fairy-tale-live-action-films-release-dates-jungle-book-2-cruella-dumbo-1201743988/ |access-date=2016-05-14 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |date=2016-04-25 |url-status=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513151039/http://deadline.com/2016/04/disney-fairy-tale-live-action-films-release-dates-jungle-book-2-cruella-dumbo-1201743988/ |archive-date=2016-05-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Fleming|first1=Mike Jr.|title=Craig Gillespie In Talks To Direct Emma Stone In 'Cruella'|url=https://deadline.com/2018/12/emma-stone-craig-gillespie-cruella-director-live-action-1202514016/|access-date=2018-12-05|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2018-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606173711/https://deadline.com/2018/12/emma-stone-craig-gillespie-cruella-director-live-action-1202514016/|archive-date=2019-06-06|url-status=no}}</ref>，該片由[[克雷格·格里斯佩|克雷格·格里斯佩]]執導。影片於2021年5月28日在美國影院和[[Disney+|Disney+]][[Disney+貴賓通道|貴賓通道]]上映，并收获好評与逾2亿全球票房<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/03/black-widow-cruella-disney-plus-theaters-day-and-date-release-1234720116/|title=Disney Shifts 'Black Widow' & 'Cruella' To Day & Date Release In Theaters And Disney+, Jarring Summer Box Office|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2021-03-23|access-date=2021-05-28|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323183840/https://deadline.com/2021/03/black-widow-cruella-disney-plus-theaters-day-and-date-release-1234720116/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CruellaNewReleaseDate">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/emma-stone-cruella-amy-adams-woman-in-the-window-disney-fox-release-date-changes-1202677451/|title=Amy Adams 'Woman In The Window' Will Now Open In Early Summer, 'Cruella' Moves To 2021|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2019-08-20|access-date=2019-08-20|archive-date=2019-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190820233429/https://deadline.com/2019/08/emma-stone-cruella-amy-adams-woman-in-the-window-disney-fox-release-date-changes-1202677451/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《洛杉矶时报》的{{Internal link helper/en|贾斯汀·张|Justin Chang}}赞赏了斯通对这位名义上的大反派的表演，称其“全心全意，魅力四射”；他亦指出斯通的表演与克洛斯在旧版电影中“尖利的”演出大相径庭，认为斯通的角色“更棘手且复杂”，且在与《真寵》的对比中指出斯通“将另一个欲成就一番事业的雄心勃勃的灰姑娘演绎得淋漓尽致”，同时表扬了她灵活游走在艾丝黛拉和库伊拉间[[变身怪医|变身怪医]]式的特质之间，尽管电影剧本本身拥有瑕疵<ref>{{Cite web|title=Review: ‘Cruella’ is dazzling fun but shows too much sympathy for the de Vil|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2021-05-26/cruella-review-disney-emma-stone-emma-thompson-101-dalmatians|access-date=2022-01-10|date=2021-05-26|last=Twitter|work=Los Angeles Times|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210530193545/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2021-05-26/cruella-review-disney-emma-stone-emma-thompson-101-dalmatians|dead-url=no}}</ref>。斯通凭借该片收获她的第六次[[金球奖|金球奖]]提名（同时也是第四次[[金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影女主角|最佳音乐及喜剧类电影女主角]]提名）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Here's the full list of 2022 Golden Globe nominations|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/awards/story/2021-12-13/2022-golden-globes-nominations-list|access-date=2022-01-10|date=2021-12-13|last=Facebook|work=Los Angeles Times|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220208021832/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/awards/story/2021-12-13/2022-golden-globes-nominations-list|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

